name: my cousing 13 years' old bear
description:
so have you heard of this 13 years guy who hates school, doesnt understand shit since pandemic happened, and can really get really angry with life?

My cousing is struggling with school but really can understand NFTs better than I do. I offered him help - I would post some of his arts in here and if it sells we are gonna full suport his art. Now he's living in Alba's Favela, in São Paulo.

Want to help? come along.
